    cl_abap_unit_assert=>assert_equals(
      act = ls_after
      exp = ls_before ).

  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD ignore.

    CONSTANTS: lc_path     TYPE string VALUE '/',
               lc_filename TYPE string VALUE 'foobar.txt'.

    DATA: lv_ignored TYPE abap_bool,
          lo_dot     TYPE REF TO lcl_dot_abapgit.


